I don't know what the other two

58:47.000 --> 58:49.000
think.

58:49.000 --> 58:51.000
He mentioned that

58:51.000 --> 58:53.000
this is related to

58:53.000 --> 58:55.000
the role we give them

58:55.000 --> 58:57.000
or their own role.

58:57.000 --> 58:59.000
What do you think

58:59.000 --> 59:01.000
about this?

59:05.000 --> 59:07.000
For example,

59:07.000 --> 59:09.000
Xiaoyu or Zashi.

