You mean

59:27.000 --> 59:29.000
if the school

59:29.000 --> 59:31.000
thinks it is

59:31.000 --> 59:33.000
a research university

59:33.000 --> 59:35.000
or a teaching university

59:35.000 --> 59:37.000
